Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.10,0:00:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.88,0:00:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就算再怎么敏捷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.56,0:00:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,火焰...闪电!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:09.62,Background,,0,0,0,,不行 不能用那招啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 得迎击...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.76,0:00:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,快躲开!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.00,0:01:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,贝尔!!
